---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import PageHero from "@components/PageHero.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About MNS1 Express | Plainfield, IL Midwest Carrier"
  description="Founded in 2011 with a single truck in Chicagoland. Today: 180+ trucks, 11 Midwest states, and a Plainfield HQ — still family-owned, still driver-first."
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="About MNS1 Express"
    title="One Truck. One Driver. One Vision."
    lead="Founded in 2011 with a single truck in Chicagoland. Today: 180+ trucks, 11 Midwest states, and a Plainfield HQ — still family-owned, still driver-first."
  />
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap stat-grid stat-grid--icons">
      <article style="text-align:center">
        <svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="display:block;width:22px;height:22px;margin:0 auto 12px;color:var(--color-blue);fill:none;stroke:currentColor;stroke-width:2;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round">
          <path d="M8 2v4" />
          <path d="M16 2v4" />
          <rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2" />
          <path d="M3 10h18" />
        </svg>
        <strong>2011</strong><span>Founded</span>
      </article>
      <article style="text-align:center">
        <svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="display:block;width:22px;height:22px;margin:0 auto 12px;color:var(--color-blue);fill:none;stroke:currentColor;stroke-width:2;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round">
          <path d="M14 18V6a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v11a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h2" />
          <path d="M15 18H9" />
          <path d="M19 18h2a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-3.65a1 1 0 0 0-.22-.62l-3.48-4.35A1 1 0 0 0 17.52 8H14" />
          <circle cx="17" cy="18" r="2" />
          <circle cx="7" cy="18" r="2" />
        </svg>
        <strong>180+</strong><span>Trucks today</span>
      </article>
      <article style="text-align:center">
        <svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="display:block;width:22px;height:22px;margin:0 auto 12px;color:var(--color-blue);fill:none;stroke:currentColor;stroke-width:2;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6" />
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2" />
        </svg>
        <strong>500</strong><span>Target fleet size</span>
      </article>
      <article style="text-align:center">
        <svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="display:block;width:22px;height:22px;margin:0 auto 12px;color:var(--color-blue);fill:none;stroke:currentColor;stroke-width:2;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round">
          <path d="M20 10c0 5-8 12-8 12S4 15 4 10a8 8 0 1 1 16 0Z" />
          <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3" />
        </svg>
        <strong>11</strong><span>Midwest states</span>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section section--panel">
    <div class="wrap split">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Our Story</p>
        <h2>From One Truck to 180+</h2>
        <p>Mike founded MNS1 Express in 2011 with a single truck in the Chicago suburbs. No investors, no fleet manager — just a driver who believed he could do it better.</p>
        <p>That one truck became two. Then ten. Then fifty. Each step was built on the same principle: treat drivers the way you'd want to be treated. Pay fairly. Keep your promises on home time. Run good equipment. Don't cut corners.</p>
        <p>In 2023, MNS1 moved to its current headquarters at 14458 S Depot Dr, Plainfield, IL 60544 — a purpose-built facility with room to grow. The fleet now runs 180+ trucks across 11 Midwest states, with a target of 500.</p>
        <p>Mike is still in the building. Not a figurehead — an operator. IT professional with 14+ years of infrastructure experience who brings that engineering mindset to every part of the business: systems, processes, decisions.</p>
      </div>
      <aside class="panel">
        <p class="eyebrow">Philosophy</p>
        <h3>1% Better Every Day</h3>
        <ul class="check-list">
          <li><strong>Always Forward</strong> Our brand is an arrow. We don't look back — we improve, adapt, and move. Every decision pushes us forward.</li>
          <li><strong>Driver-First Decisions</strong> Equipment, pay, home time, policies — we make choices from the driver's seat. If it doesn't work for drivers, it doesn't work for us.</li>
          <li><strong>The Explorer Archetype</strong> We're not the biggest. We're the ones willing to explore new territory — in technology, in operations, in how a carrier should treat its people.</li>
          <li><strong>No Shortcuts</strong> 180+ trucks built without cutting corners on safety, equipment, or people. The plan to 500 follows the same playbook.</li>
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap split">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Headquarters</p>
        <h2>Plainfield, Illinois</h2>
        <p>MNS1 Express Inc.<br />14458 S Depot Dr<br />Plainfield, IL 60544</p>
      </div>
      <aside class="panel">
        <h3>Join the MNS1 Team</h3>
        <p>CDL-A, 24+ months experience. Apply in 4 mins. Orientation in Plainfield.</p>
        <p><a class="text-link" href="tel:6302463280">630-246-3280</a></p>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
